---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Suppression list">
  <h1>Suppression list</h1>

  <p>The suppression list is a record of email addresses that should NOT receive non-transactional mail. Hard bounces, spam reports, and one-click unsubscribes auto-write here.</p>
  <h2>Transactional bypass</h2>
  <p>Account-related mail (invitation, password reset, registration confirmation) BYPASSES the suppression list per CAN-SPAM transactional exemption.</p>
  <h2>Manual add / remove</h2>
  <p>Site Settings → Email → Suppression list. Manual remove warns about CAN-SPAM compliance — only remove an address when the user has explicitly asked to re-subscribe.</p>
</BaseLayout>
